snippet.title: The Sims 4 Get to Work: Official Retail Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Create and manage your own unique retail business in a brand new neighborhood in The Sims 4 Get to Work Expansion Pack.

Learn more: http://bit.ly/1NEJOwX

Actively control your Sims at their workplace in The Sims 4 Get to Work, available April 2015.
